This project analyzes pizza sales data to uncover insights that can help improve business performance. The dashboard highlights sales trends, customer preferences, and product performance. It was built by cleaning and preparing raw data using SQL and visualizing key insights using Tableau.

ğŸ¯ Objectives

Identify the best-performing pizzas by revenue and quantity sold.

Detect the worst-performing pizzas that may need marketing adjustments or menu reconsideration.

Analyze daily and monthly sales trends to understand peak demand periods.

Provide data-driven insights to improve overall sales strategy.

