ğŸ“Š Key Insights from the Dashboard

The top 5 pizzas account for a significant share of total revenue.

Certain pizza categories (like Large & XL sizes) drive more profit compared to smaller ones.

Sales peak during weekends and evenings, showing strong demand patterns.

A few pizza types consistently underperform, suggesting opportunities for menu optimization.

